vim for coding in terminal{
$vim filename.js   for Javascript
$vim filename.py   for python
$vim filename.c    for C
........

you have to enter Insert mode first By pressing  ---> i   in keyboard  or o but it will create a new line
then Exit insert mode for Another commands --->  ESC

:W for save the file
:q to exit the editor
:wq for save and exit at the same time

:syntax on
:set number    to add line number you have to do it everytime when you join vim mode

 i or o again to join insert mode

}
